traits.name: Overcrowded
traits.description: A waypoint teeming with inhabitants, leading to cramped living conditions and a high demand for resources.

traits.name: High-Tech
traits.description: A center of innovation and cutting-edge technology, driving progress and attracting skilled individuals from around the galaxy.

traits.name: Bureaucratic
traits.description: A waypoint governed by complex regulations, red tape, and layers of administration, often leading to inefficiencies and frustration.

traits.name: Temperate
traits.description: A world with a mild climate and balanced ecosystem, providing a comfortable environment for a variety of life forms and supporting diverse industries.

traits.name: Marketplace
traits.description: A thriving center of commerce where traders from across the galaxy gather to buy, sell, and exchange goods.
